		{
			title: "Naga! - Twilight"
			x: -4.0d
			y: 0.0d
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "The Snake. Left Click for more info"
			description: ["It can be found in the Naga Courtyard. The Naga is a large snake-like creature, and deals 9 (Heart.svgHeart.svgHeart.svgHeart.svgHalf Heart.svg) points of damage when attacking and has 250 (Heart.svg × 125) health points. As the Naga sustains damage it will lose its large segments and move faster. If it is not attacked for a while it will begin to heal itself. The Naga is bound to its Courtyard and will lose interest if its targets move out of it."]
