		{
			title: "The Castle"
			x: 8.5d
			y: 0.0d
			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "Reaching the Castle will give you a nice reward. While holding the Earth Talisman in your inventory, it will give you the Geomancy effect, which will allow you to basically become Toph Beifong. If you have no idea who that is, too bad. Well, not really. It will allow you to throw and manipulate dirt blocks in a very cool way. Right-click to pick up blocks and shift right-click to pick up entire boulders. Left-click to push them forward"
			dependencies: ["211035352B304A68"]
